          "id": 57781,
          "text": "<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Vigabatrin decreases GABA uptake at the synaptic cleft. </span></span></span></p>"
        },
        {
          "id": 57782,
